        "\n",
        "## Forecasting with ARIMA {#sec-arimaforecast}\n",
        "\n",
        "### How Integration Changes the Forecast\n",
        "\n",
        "An ARMA model forecasts levels directly — the $h$-step forecast pulls toward\n",
        "the unconditional mean as the horizon grows, and prediction intervals eventually\n",
        "plateau at the unconditional variance. An ARIMA model works differently. Because\n",
