        "3 and 4. Start at the top and follow the branches based on what the data show.\n",
        "Every endpoint names the model family and notes the X extension; if economic\n",
        "theory suggests a relevant $I(0)$ exogenous variable, add it at any endpoint.\n",
        "If the regressor is itself $I(1)$, consider VECM (Chapter 7) instead.\n",
        "\n",
